<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Meta Information -->
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0"
    />
    <title>Home Page</title>

    <!-- External CSS -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.min.css"
      type="text/css"
    />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bungee&family=Source+Sans+Pro:ital,wght@0,300;0,600;1,300;1,600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- App CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/layout.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/like__btn.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/nav.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/header.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/collab.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/back-to-top.css" type="text/css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="/styles/responsive-design.css"
      type="text/css"
    />

    <!-- External JS -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <!-- App JS -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/client.js"></script>
    <script
      type="text/javascript"
      src="/scripts/composer-char-counter.js"
    ></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/back-to-top.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/compose.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/nav.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/like__btn.js"></script>

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
  </head>

  <!-- CDN: timeago -->
  <script
    src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/timeago.js/4.0.2/timeago.min.js"
    integrity="sha512-SVDh1zH5N9ChofSlNAK43lcNS7lWze6DTVx1JCXH1Tmno+0/1jMpdbR8YDgDUfcUrPp1xyE53G42GFrcM0CMVg=="
    crossorigin="anonymous"
    referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
  ></script>

  <body>
    <!-- Top nav bar (fixed) -->
    <%- include('partials/_nav') %>

    <!-- Header (fixed)-->
    <%- include('partials/_header') %>

    <!-- Page-specific (main) content here -->
    <main class="container">
      <!-- COMPLETED STORIES -->
      <section class="completed">
        <h1>Completed Stories</h1>
        <article class="story-container">
          <header>
            <span id="user-name">username</span>
          </header>
          <p class="story-content">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec at
            dapibus est, id faucibus orci. Quisque eget semper odio. Fusce
            porttitor placerat sem, ac semper metus malesuada eu. Mauris massa
            urna, facilisis sit amet ultrices eu, mollis eget diam. Etiam vel
            nisi et leo accumsan cursus. Proin gravida volutpat velit ac
            commodo. Vivamus sed posuere nisi. Sed pellentesque hendrerit
            mattis. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia
            nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Pellentesque ornare dictum dapibus.
            Nullam accumsan varius turpis quis ultricies. Quisque sodales tortor
            ac tortor ultrices, quis aliquet erat feugiat. Suspendisse a sem
            rhoncus, eleifend dui a, luctus felis. Class aptent taciti sociosqu
            ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos.
          </p>
          <section class="new-collab">
            <section class="error-message"></section>
            <!-- User input story form -->
            <form class="collab-form">
              <textarea
                name="text"
                id="collab-text"
                placeholder="What are you humming about?"
              ></textarea>
              <!-- Submit story -->
              <button id="collab-button" type="submit">Submit</button>
              <!-- Count characters of collab -->
              <output name="counter" class="counter" for="collab-text">140</output>
            </form>
            <!-- Render collab -->
            <section class="collab-section"></section>
          </section>

    </main>
    <button class="back-to-top">
      <i class="fas fa-angle-double-up" id="arrow-up"></i>
    </button>
  </body>
</html>
